summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the condemnation proceedings to acquire real property and real property rights necessary for the Southwest Kenyon Street et al., Sanitary Sewer Project for sewer purposes under Ordinance 106264, King County Superior Court Cause No. 829728; accepting condemnation awards for Parcels 7272-41, 7272-94 and 7272-140 in connection therewith, and making an appropriation from the Municipal Sewerage 1971 Construction Fund therefor.
